article.headline: UTEP 65, UAB 37
article.story: EL PASO, Texas (AP) -- John Tofi scored 14 points and grabbed 15 rebounds to lead Texas-El Paso to a 65-37 victory over UAB Wednesday night. The Miners (14-6, 7-1 Conference USA) led throughout the game, including a game-high 31-point lead with 1:13 remaining. Jason Williams added 14 points and nine rebounds for UTEP, and Edgar Moreno scored 11. Carldell Johnson led UAB (16-5, 6-2) with 10 points. He was the only UAB player to score in double digits. UTEP had 14 points off turnovers, while UAB had eight. UTEP led 34-18 at halftime.
